@startuml

actor User
participant "Allergy App" as App
participant "Nearby User" as NearbyUser

User -> App: Open app
App -> App: Show Home Screen
User -> App: Select "Receive Alert from Nearby User"
App -> App: Retrieve Nearby User Alert
App -> NearbyUser: Request Nearby User Alert
NearbyUser -> App: Send Nearby User Alert
App --> User: Display Nearby User Alert

@enduml
